# IndexTTS Batch GUI

A Python desktop app for batch voice generation through an IndexTTS WebUI endpoint.

## Features

- Configurable WebUI host and port
- Task set directories with persistent JSON tasks
- Task-level text, reference audio, and synthesis config
- Defaults for new tasks and multiline text expansion
- Batch execution with per-task progress/state
- Regeneration replaces old audio and updates task JSON
- Per-task audio playback after success

## Quick start

```bash
pip install -e .[dev]
python -m indextts_batch_gui
```

## Tests

```bash
pytest
```

## Build executable (Windows)

```powershell
scripts\build_windows.ps1
```
